parameters: Do you want to enter the boss area?
Clea (Let's prepare first before doing that)

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: After the Imperial Army,
now it's monsters... my luck is terrible.

Thief Nora: I won't let you lay a finger on them! I'll be
your opponent!

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Phew... Thanks to you, I
was saved. I never thought the day would come when Nora
would save my life.
Thief Nora: Hehe, I think I've grown too, maybe.
Clea: Are there any other injured people?

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: As long as I meet the
other five, I'll be fine.

Priestess Sophia: In that case, there's no problem. I will
perform healing on you, the last injured person.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: I fought against General
Atu's subordinates, but it seemed like they were holding
back quite a bit.

Mage Relm: No matter what, that person is a kind-hearted
individual! If things continue like this, it seems like they
might become our ally!

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: That's absolutely not
true... Besides General Atu's subordinates, they're here to
kill us.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Nora, do you remember?
About Sid, who was good at baking bread.

Thief Nora: Of course! I absolutely love Sid's bread, you
know!
Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: I was killed.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Even though I'm not a
combatant, the leader prioritized saving Sid from the
hideout.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Afterwards, there was a
corpse lying in the bandit's grassland. It was covered in
wounds, they must have been tortured relentlessly.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Nora, it would be better
for you not to get involved anymore. You should leave the
campus and hide somewhere.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: I'll leave this ring with
you. It's a memento that Sid cherished.

Injured Emma Thief Guild Member: Thank you for saving me.
Maybe it would have been better if I had been eaten here, it
might have been happier.
Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan... Are you okay?

Thief Nora: *sniffle*... I'm okay! I'll definitely rescue
them!

Thief Nora: I haven't been able to repay the favor of being
saved by everyone in the Emma Thief Guild.

Thief Nora: So please help me! Please fight together with
me to save my comrades!
Clea: Of course, I will fight for Nora-san's sake.

Mage Relm: There's no problem that can't be solved if the
great genius cooperates, right?

Priestess Sophia: Of course, Nora-chan. We are your
allies.

Thief Nora (Guild Master, please wait. I will definitely
save everyone in the Emma Thief Guild!)
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
